## 2. Authoritative Overrides (These Beat the RAD/RDD)

| RAD/RDD Says | Build This Instead |
|---|---|
| YOLOv8 for visual detection | `dino_v3_linear.pth` — team-provided custom weights, loaded with PyTorch |
| "The team will train a custom model" | The model file is provided. Just load it. Do not retrain. |
| Surgical Gaussian blur over detected coordinates | Full `filter: blur(24px)` on entire `<video>` (extension) / full-screen `BackdropFilter` overlay (Android) |
| iOS custom browser + Network Extension | Not implemented — Android only |
| Flutter for both Android and iOS | Flutter for Android only |
| TMDb API live integration | Stub only — returns ALLOW until API key is set |
| Cloud deployment of backend | `localhost:8000` only during development |
| Violence / Kissing / Profanity / LGBTQ models | Stubs returning `detected: false` — same interface as nudity module |

