## 11. Testing Requirements

### Backend (pytest)
- Test `/health` returns 200 and correct JSON shape
- Test `/analyze-image` with a blank white JPEG returns valid response shape
- Test BR-01: sensitivity=0.1 still results in effective_threshold=0.75
- Test stub modules return `detected: false` always

### Extension (Jest)
- `videoMonitor`: confirms `<video>` elements are found after DOM insertion
- `blurManager`: confirms `filter: blur(24px)` is applied and removed correctly
- `serviceWorker`: mock fetch, confirm BLUR message is sent on `detected: true`
- `businessRules`: confirm BR-01 threshold floor

### Android (Flutter test)
- `SettingsService`: write and read back all settings correctly
- `AiClient`: mock HTTP, confirm correct request shape and response parsing
- `BlurOverlay` widget: renders when `isBlurred=true`, hidden when `false`

